{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset was split into 9,000 training samples, 1,855 validation samples, and 1,855 testing samples.",
    "The RoBERTa model achieved an accuracy rate of 93.8% on the testing set, which outperformed several state-of-the-art sentiment analysis models, including BERT and XLNet.",
    "The RoBERTa model was also evaluated on its ability to detect sarcasm in text data using the SARC dataset, which contains sarcastic and non-sarcastic examples.",
    "The model achieved an accuracy of 89.5% on the testing set, which outperformed several state-of-the-art sarcasm detection models, including LSTM and CNN-based models.",
    "Overall, the RoBERTa pre-trained model demonstrated excellent performance in sentiment analysis and sarcasm detection tasks."
  ]
}